Class GnUserStore

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
IGnUserStore
public class GnUserStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGnUserStore

Store and load serialized GnUser using Shared Preferences. This is a Gracenote helper delegate class to store and load the Gracenote serialized user. It uses Shared Preferences to persist the user data. For all helper delegate classes you can provide your own implementation, it just needs to implement the correct interface, in this case IGnUserStore. If you do provide your own implementation Gracenote recommends starting with this implementation and altering as required; therefore the source is available on request.
